window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Mars is gone, my friends are in need of a rescue, and I’m running out of options unless I do something monumentally dangerous.</b></p> <p>Turns out, that’s my specialty.</p> <p>When the dust settled, humanity’s greatest stronghold was nothing but rubble. They took Rachel. They took Stormfall. They took everyone I cared about, and they left me alive.</p> <p>Big mistake.</p> <p>To save my friends, I’ll fight through alien death ships, outsmart a traitor who sold us out, and probably set something important on fire.</p> <p>And if I’m lucky—if I don’t die horribly—I might just send the Gehenna a message they’ll never forget.</p> <p>A marine’s work is never done.</p>"; 
